tasks.description:
Add GET /api/projects/{id}/fingerprint handler. Looks up fingerprint from SpacetimeDB by project_id. Returns JSON fingerprint or 404 if not generated yet. Also add GET /api/projects/{id}/fingerprint/text that returns the formatted injection block as plain text (for direct system prompt prepending). The text format: '## Project Architecture Context
Language: {language} | Style: {architecture_style} | Framework: {framework}
Objective: {workplan_objective}
Constraints:
- {constraint1}
- ...
Active ADRs: {adr_summaries}
---'. Done when: cargo build passes and both endpoints return correct data.
